Advanced Model Recommendations

Based on current analysis, these additional models could improve prediction accuracy:

  • XGBoost - Typically outperforms Random Forest for time series data with ~5-15% accuracy improvement
  • LSTM Neural Networks - Can identify complex temporal patterns (~10-20% potential improvement)
  • CatBoost - Handles categorical features (like day of week) particularly well
  • Ensemble Methods - Combining RandomForest, GradientBoosting and LogisticRegression could increase accuracy by ~7%
  • Prophet - Facebook's time series forecasting tool with built-in seasonality handling
  • ARIMA - Classic time series model for trend and seasonality analysis

See the "Advanced ML" tab for implementation of these models!

Advanced Machine Learning Analysis

Advanced Model Performance

XGBoost Feature Importance

Prophet Model Forecast

Advanced Model Features

XGBoost & CatBoost
  • Gradient boosting algorithms optimized for structured data
  • Handle complex non-linear relationships
  • CatBoost specially designed for categorical features (like day of week)
  • Improved handling of missing values and outliers
LSTM Neural Networks
  • Deep learning models that recognize patterns in sequences
  • Can capture long-term dependencies in time series data
  • Effective at learning complex market behaviors
  • Particularly good at capturing regime changes
Prophet
  • Facebook's time series forecasting library
  • Automatically handles seasonality, holidays, and trend changes
  • Decomposition of trends from daily, weekly, and yearly patterns
  • Robust to missing data and outliers
ARIMA
  • Classic time series forecasting model
  • Captures autoregressive and moving average components
  • Well-established statistical foundation
  • Effective at capturing short-term behaviors
